query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 10 AND q.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('app-store',
'c++14',
'etl',
'global-variables',
'java-ee',
'jtable',
'nokogiri',
'resharper',
'themes',
'transactions',
'uiimageview',
'woocommerce');
